#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Quarkus 3.26 - Hibernate updates, named persistence units in Hibernate Reactive, Dev UI as MCP functions, and more."
msgstr ""

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Today, we released Quarkus 3.26. It comes with an update of the Hibernate stack, support for named persistence units in Hibernate Reactive, Dev UI capabilities exposed as MCP functions, and more."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid ""
"Quarkus 3.26 is an important milestone towards our next LTS release:\n"
"it marks the feature freeze for Quarkus 3.27 LTS, which will be based on 3.26 and released at the end of September."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "We urge you to upgrade to this release and report any issues you may find, so we can address them before the LTS release."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Quarkus 3.26 introduces the following notable changes:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/49429[#49429] - Update to Hibernate ORM 7.1, Hibernate Search 8.1, and Hibernate Reactive 3.1"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/48007[#48007] - Support named persistence units and data sources in Hibernate Reactive"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/49408[#49408] - Offline startup and dialect configuration for Hibernate ORM"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/49165[#49165] - Dev UI HQL console redesign + Hibernate Assistant functionality"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/47414[#47414] - Expose Dev UI's capabilities as MCP functions"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/49003[#49003] - OIDC Client filter - allow to trigger token refresh when REST client request results in 401"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/49042[#49042] - Support for customizing request and response body in OIDC filters"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/48687[#48687] - Add functionality to capture Quarkus application runtime data using JFR extension"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/49256[#49256] - Bump Gradle version to 9.0"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid ""
"In addition, Quarkus 3.26 drops support for legacy config classes entirely, so make sure you update your third-party extensions to the latest,\n"
"as their new versions should already have been moved to `@ConfigMapping` interfaces."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Update"
msgstr "Atualização"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To update to Quarkus 3.26, we recommend updating to the latest version of the Quarkus CLI and run:"
msgstr "Para atualizar para o Quarkus 3.26, recomendamos atualizar para a versão mais recente do Quarkus CLI e executar:"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Note that `quarkus update` can update your applications from any version of Quarkus (including 2.x) to Quarkus 3.26."
msgstr "Observe que `o quarkus update` pode atualizar seus aplicativos de qualquer versão do Quarkus (incluindo a 2.x) para o Quarkus 3.26."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For more information about the adjustments you need to make to your applications, please refer to the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.26[Quarkus 3.26 migration guide]."
msgstr "Para obter mais informações sobre os ajustes que o senhor precisa fazer em seus aplicativos, consulte o link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.26[guia de migração do Quarkus 3.26] ."

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What's new?"
msgstr "O que é que há de novo?"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hibernate"
msgstr "Hibernar"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "The Hibernate extensions got several improvements in this release:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "We updated to Hibernate ORM 7.1, Hibernate Search 8.1, and Hibernate Reactive 3.1"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "The Hibernate Reactive extension now supports named persistence units and data sources - which was a long-awaited feature"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "The Hibernate ORM extension now supports offline startup and dialect configuration - which allows to start up even if the database is not reachable at startup time"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "The Dev UI HQL console has been redesigned and now includes Hibernate Assistant functionality: we are looking forward to your feedback on this new feature!"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Dev UI"
msgstr "Interface do usuário do desenvolvedor"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid ""
"Apart from the improvements mentioned above, we started exposing the Dev UI's capabilities as MCP functions,\n"
"meaning you can now pilot the Dev UI from your favorite AI tooling."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "OIDC"
msgstr "OIDC"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "The OIDC extension now allows to trigger token refresh when a REST client request results in 401."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Also, you can now customize the request and response body in OIDC filters."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "JFR"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Using the JFR extension, you can now capture Quarkus application runtime data such as application name, application version, and the list of active extensions."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Gradle"
msgstr "Gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "The Gradle version used by default when creating a new project has been bumped to 9.0."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2025-08-28-quarkus-3-26-released.adoc
msgid "Gradle 8.14 is still supported but some earlier 8.x versions might not work anymore, due to the changes we made to support Gradle 9."
msgstr ""

